com.vorlonsoft.android.rate

Class DefaultDialogManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vorlonsoft.android.rate.DefaultDialogManager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DialogManager
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AppCompatDialogManager

    public class DefaultDialogManager
extends Object
implements DialogManager

    DefaultDialogManager Class - default dialog manager class implements DialogManager interface of the AndroidRate library.

    You can extend DefaultDialogManager Class and use AppRate.setDialogManagerFactory(DialogManager.Factory) if you want to use fully custom dialog (from v7 AppCompat library etc.). DefaultDialogManager Class is thread-safe and a fast singleton implementation inside library, not outside (protected, not private constructor).

    Since:
    1.0.2
